- Sentry trpcMiddleware source: `getsentry/sentry-javascript/packages/core/src/trpc.ts`
- Sentry discussion on noise: `getsentry/sentry-javascript#10748`
- tRPC onError ctx limitation: `trpc/trpc#6157`

